title: For Sale:  Old DoubleTap full strength 10mm 180gr. JHP
postcontent:
For sale: Old DoubleTap full strength 10mm ammo. This ammo has more feet pounds of energy and a higher velocity than the current loadings by the bigger manufacturers. I would advise against using this in smaller pistols or using this to train new shooters since this is loaded to near .41 Magnum specifications. Most modern 10mm is loaded to the same power as .40S&W, this DoubleTap is what 10mm was originally designed to be.

This is older stock that I bought for my Bren Ten several years ago, it's mostly 180gr JHP in plain 50 round boxes. I'm asking $50 per box, have up to 20 available (1000 rounds). If you're not happy with pricing feel free to make offers if you're willing to buy that same day. Worst I can do is say no. All deals will be in the quiet suburbs outside Baltimore.

I have several hundred feedback (all positive) between eBay, gunbroker, and many gun and vehicle related forums. This said, I will see to it that everything on my end goes smoothly. The rest is up to you.
